---
import { CONTACT_EMAIL } from '../utils/constants';
---

<!-- Investment Perspective + Final CTA -->
<section id="inquire" class="border-t border-slate-800">
  <!-- Investment Perspective -->
  <div class="max-w-screen-xl mx-auto px-8 py-20">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-900 to-slate-950 border border-slate-700 rounded-3xl p-10 md:p-14">
        <div class="uppercase tracking-[1.5px] text-xs font-semibold text-amber-400 mb-4">PREMIUM DOMAIN ACQUISITION</div>

        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold tracking-tighter mb-6">A strategic asset in a defining industry shift.</h2>

        <div class="copy-text space-y-5 text-[15.2px]">
          <p>Premium domains at the intersection of AI and creative technology have demonstrated strong acquisition values in recent transactions. Names that clearly signal category leadership and brand potential consistently outperform generic alternatives.</p>

          <p>voiceversehub.com combines three powerful elements rarely found together in a single, clean .com:</p>

          <ul class="space-y-2 pl-1">
            <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-indigo-400 font-mono text-sm mt-1">01</span> <span>Descriptive precision that owns the narrative</span></li>
            <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-indigo-400 font-mono text-sm mt-1">02</span> <span>Poetic resonance that creates emotional connection</span></li>
            <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-indigo-400 font-mono text-sm mt-1">03</span> <span>Platform-level scalability for ambitious execution</span></li>
          </ul>

          <p class="pt-3">Whether you are an entrepreneur building the category leader, an investor assembling a portfolio of high-conviction digital assets, or a company seeking a powerful brand foundation, this domain represents a rare opportunity to secure the name that defines the new creative stack.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-9 pt-8 border-t border-slate-700 flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-center gap-y-4 justify-between">
          <div>
            <div class="text-xs text-slate-500">SUITABLE FOR</div>
            <div class="text-sm font-medium">Visionary founders &bull; AI-native brands &bull; Strategic investors &bull; Creative technology companies</div>
          </div>
          <div class="text-xs px-4 py-2 bg-slate-800 rounded-2xl inline-flex items-center text-slate-400 border border-slate-700">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-info-circle mr-2 text-indigo-400"></i>
            <span>Serious inquiries only</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Final CTA -->
  <div class="bg-slate-950">
    <div class="max-w-screen-xl mx-auto px-8 py-16">
      <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto text-center">
        <div class="mb-4">
          <span class="inline-block px-5 py-1.5 text-xs font-semibold tracking-[1.5px] rounded-3xl border border-indigo-500/40 text-indigo-400">AVAILABLE FOR ACQUISITION</span>
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-5xl font-bold tracking-tighter mb-4">Own the voice of the future.</h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-slate-300">voiceversehub.com is ready for the builder who will define the next chapter of AI-powered creation.</p>

        <div class="mt-10">
          <a href={`mailto:${CONTACT_EMAIL}?subject=Inquiry%20for%20voiceversehub.com`}
             class="group inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-x-4 px-10 py-5 rounded-3xl bg-white hover:bg-slate-100 active:bg-slate-200 transition-all text-slate-900 font-semibold text-lg shadow-2xl shadow-indigo-500/40">
            <span>Begin the Conversation</span>
            <i class="fa-solid fa-envelope group-active:translate-x-0.5 transition-transform"></i>
          </a>
        </div>

        <p class="mt-8 text-xs text-slate-500 max-w-xs mx-auto">All inquiries are confidential. Premium positioning. We work with serious buyers and their representatives.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
